{"tid":2331714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警員花園街 full gear 上樓　尋失蹤武肺病人","createTime":"2020-12-19T04:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T09:52:43.000Z","uid":271829,"like":19,"dislike":174,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"195482a332ba5b529b1ae951c84df9cbc31f8bbf","tid":2331714,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:28:48.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n伊利沙伯醫院一名確診武漢肺炎的63歲男病人（個案編號：7379），昨午約5時從醫院逃走，展開「流亡」生涯，院方報警處理。警方今日派員到病人報稱的住所巡視，暫時仍未有發現。<br />\n男病人由周一起入住伊院隔離病房接受治療，他確診前報住旺角花園街198號。4名警員今早10時許乘坐警車去到男病人花園街的住所，其中兩名警員身穿全套高規格的白色生化保護袍，另兩名則戴上面罩口罩及披上普通藍色保護袍。<br />\n兩名白袍警員與一名藍袍警員一起上樓巡查，但未發現男病人行蹤，而另一名警員則在大廈地下出入口把守。4人在大廈逗留約一個小時後離開。有街坊表示，警方昨晚都有派員到大廈內調查，但未有帶走任何人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1jgju1vbu0tVgjWU3fgemH0pJjo=/1017x749/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3W4S23VVGJDBTPHADI24GRYSQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1jgju1vbu0tVgjWU3fgemH0pJjo%3D%2F1017x749%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3W4S23VVGJDBTPHADI24GRYSQM.jpg&h=eacb6c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩名白袍警員與一名藍袍警員一起上樓巡查，但未發現男病人行蹤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sTmBPHwfK33-_y_cl16GBT1_cOk=/1455x868/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MDYXLCGLLRGMZFBK3GFGGNWKYQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsTmBPHwfK33-_y_cl16GBT1_cOk%3D%2F1455x868%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMDYXLCGLLRGMZFBK3GFGGNWKYQ.jpg&h=f5355311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名警員則在大廈地下出入口把守。<br />\n<br />\n流亡中的男病人身高約1.6米，中等身材及蓄黑色短髮，離院時身穿病人服、深藍色外套及運動鞋，有佩戴外科口罩。院方呼籲公眾若發現有關病人，請通知警方或致電3506 8944。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201219/LKO5VETCFZGINLGRKBJELSLBFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201219%2FLKO5VETCFZGINLGRKBJELSLBFE%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBTe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=4c057bf2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201219%2FLKO5VETCFZGINLGRKBJELSLBFE%2F&h=1de92bd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201219/LKO5VETCFZGINLGRKBJELSLBFE/</a>"},{"pid":"05844b035a4c2c0eaeb12311962813545e051e58","tid":2331714,"uid":204539,"like":243,"dislike":2,"score":241,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:30:35.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong>流亡</strong></span>中的男病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235d0a4eea3db6066e2c8c8ac77b200065aecd42","tid":2331714,"uid":84102,"like":221,"dislike":3,"score":218,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"流亡精神病領袖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa7ffd306e1202cf74d24319df380f592a087ee","tid":2331714,"uid":369011,"like":142,"dislike":5,"score":137,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"有心走佬點會返屋企咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d962a70170bc6cc14a8a8649504eea4fe928c2e","tid":2331714,"uid":220853,"like":197,"dislike":2,"score":195,"quote":{"pid":"bfa7ffd306e1202cf74d24319df380f592a087ee","tid":2331714,"uid":369011,"like":142,"dislike":5,"score":137,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"有心走佬點會返屋企咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:35:06.000Z","msg":"好難講呀呢d廢老<br />\n我諗佢最大機會係去左返工"},{"pid":"94e640639528843928f8a1c0f36346cf33d223e8","tid":2331714,"uid":301666,"like":55,"dislike":3,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:35:16.000Z","msg":"啲狗唔係好鍾意用CCTV搵人㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fbf528cdb3706f4b021d7a36ff2cc5b3c6ed66","tid":2331714,"uid":284699,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":